This is a file to update all the principal packages.
In each package it is necessary to assess which dependencies are updated and which are outdated and make a decision if it is worth.

# Packages from guppy_prokaion.py

## NanoPack

pip install nanopack --upgrade

# Packages from varcal_prokaion.py

## Minimap2

conda install -c bioconda -c conda-forge -c defaults -c r minimap2

## Samtools

conda install -c bioconda -c conda-forge -c defaults -c r samtools

## Freebayes

conda install -c bioconda -c conda-forge -c defaults -c r freebayes

## BCFtools

conda install -c bioconda -c conda-forge -c defaults -c r bcftools

## Snippy

conda install -c bioconda -c conda-forge -c defaults -c r snippy

